author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, Michelle Obama launched a podcast this week to much fanfare. The trans activist Dylan Mulvaney launched his new book in the same week. Both have been complete, humiliating flops. What does that tell us about the Left’s broader problems in the culture? Also, President Trump has a plan to eliminate taxes for everyone making under 150 thousand dollars a year. I have some issues with that, which I’ll explain. A member of a health board in Oregon identifies as a turtle, so obviously, we need to talk about that. And an official with the FAA helped non-white applicants cheat on their entrance exam. Of course, he still has a job.
